Benchmark
=========

A developer friendly profiling class. Generates plain-text formatted output indicating passed time in the nearest human unit (microseconds, seconds and minutes).

Example
=======

<?php
	include 'Benchmark.php';

	$benchmark = new Benchmark();
	$benchmark->start('SECTION');
	// do stuff
	$benchmark->stop('SECTION');

	$benchmark->display();

Output:
SECTION = 100 ms (or 1.23 s)